set -e

startTime=`date +%s.%N`
echo "StartTime: $startTime" > m64020_190210_035026.subreads.ccs.uncorrected.aligned.merged.timingInformation.txt

gatk --java-options "-Xmx130048m -DGATK_STACKTRACE_ON_USER_EXCEPTION=true" \
   PrintReads \
       -I gs://broad-dsde-methods-kiran/workflow_output/CorrectAndAlignWorkflow/e13c74a8-8bd4-4ec4-84ae-96cc5e12bf67/call-MergeRemaining/m64020_190210_035026.subreads.ccs.uncorrected.aligned.merged.bam \
       -O m64020_190210_035026.subreads.ccs.uncorrected.aligned.merged.chr1.bam \
       -RF PrimaryLineReadFilter \
       -L chr1

endTime=`date +%s.%N`
echo "EndTime: $endTime" >> m64020_190210_035026.subreads.ccs.uncorrected.aligned.merged.timingInformation.txt
elapsedTime=`python -c "print( $endTime - $startTime )"`

GetZmwCounts.PrintReadsTask.commandLine:
set -e

startTime=`date +%s.%N`
echo "StartTime: $startTime" > m64020_190210_035026.subreads.ccs.uncorrected.aligned.merged.timingInformation.txt

gatk --java-options "-Xmx130048m -DGATK_STACKTRACE_ON_USER_EXCEPTION=true" \
   PrintReads \
       -I gs://broad-dsde-methods-kiran/workflow_output/CorrectAndAlignWorkflow/e13c74a8-8bd4-4ec4-84ae-96cc5e12bf67/call-MergeRemaining/m64020_190210_035026.subreads.ccs.uncorrected.aligned.merged.bam \
       -O m64020_190210_035026.subreads.ccs.uncorrected.aligned.merged.chr4.bam \
       -RF PrimaryLineReadFilter \
       -L chr4

endTime=`date +%s.%N`
echo "EndTime: $endTime" >> m64020_190210_035026.subreads.ccs.uncorrected.aligned.merged.timingInformation.txt
elapsedTime=`python -c "print( $endTime - $startTime )"`
echo "Elapsed Time: $elapsedTime" >> m64020_190210_035026.subreads.ccs.uncorrected.aligned.merged.timingInformation.txt

   PrintReads \
       -I gs://broad-dsde-methods-kiran/workflow_output/CorrectAndAlignWorkflow/e13c74a8-8bd4-4ec4-84ae-96cc5e12bf67/call-MergeRemaining/m64020_190210_035026.subreads.ccs.uncorrected.aligned.merged.bam \
       -O m64020_190210_035026.subreads.ccs.uncorrected.aligned.merged.chr15.bam \
       -RF PrimaryLineReadFilter \
       -L chr15

endTime=`date +%s.%N`
echo "EndTime: $endTime" >> m64020_190210_035026.subreads.ccs.uncorrected.aligned.merged.timingInformation.txt
elapsedTime=`python -c "print( $endTime - $startTime )"`

gatk --java-options "-Xmx130048m -DGATK_STACKTRACE_ON_USER_EXCEPTION=true" \
   PrintReads \
       -I gs://broad-dsde-methods-kiran/workflow_output/CorrectAndAlignWorkflow/e13c74a8-8bd4-4ec4-84ae-96cc5e12bf67/call-MergeRemaining/m64020_190210_035026.subreads.ccs.uncorrected.aligned.merged.bam \
       -O m64020_190210_035026.subreads.ccs.uncorrected.aligned.merged.chr21.bam \
       -RF PrimaryLineReadFilter \
       -L chr21

endTime=`date +%s.%N`
echo "EndTime: $endTime" >> m64020_190210_035026.subreads.ccs.uncorrected.aligned.merged.timingInformation.txt
elapsedTime=`python -c "print( $endTime - $startTime )"`

elapsedTime=`python -c "print( $endTime - $startTime )"`
